      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances luxury and daily utility. The exterior retains a brilliant, deep luster, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple and free of tears, showing only light, natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the high-fidelity audio system, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a comprehensive service history that documents its mechanical health. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a turn-key car that has been cared for with pride, offering a refined driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
